{
  "stem": "22734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And by that time, he believed it, because the men left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if they don't go through the selection, they could go and die with their children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Nobody made any bones about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In plain language.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were 1,000 children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And three mothers didn't go with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So that's remarkable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I loved them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, but I-- I-- I wasn't their mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked with the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I taught them how to read and write.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A group of children, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- we divided them by age into small groups, into groups who-- who-- just a play school and some were older children-- I mean, older, eight year old, nine year old, six year old, we tried to teach how to read and write from little things that the men or the people who worked in the-- in the central warehouse where all the things from the people who came from all over the world were stored.",
      "word_count": 77
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was called Kanada.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- they brought us books, some books.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that-- it was unlimited there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were sorting the clothes and they were being packed to Germany, for people who were bombed out or for-- they called it winter help, the help for the winter.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was all going back to the Reich, what they took from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the gold that they found, that was going into the Reich's bank, to the central bank in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and the gold teeth that they took out because once the people were gassed, so there was a commander that didn't do anything but took out-- opened their mouth and took out the gold teeth, gold-- everything, you know, with pliers.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was also sent, then, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
